Package Objects

Class MovieTicket

Object
MovieTicket
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MovieTicket extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a MovieTicket / Movie Booking. Each seat booked at a cinema corresponds to a MovieTicket.
Since:
2022-11-11
Version:
1.0
Author:
Chay Hui Xiang
